@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_nolydh(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.abs(0.05)
    v0 = (0.59 - v1)
    tmp = v2
    tmp = (0.23 - (tmp + wp.sin(v2 + 0.00)))
    v1 = wp.cos(((v1 + 0.13 * tmp + 0.27) / 0.62))
    v1 = tmp
    v1 = wp.abs(v2)
    v1 = wp.sin((wp.sin(v1 + 0.00) / (v1 + 0.58 + v1 + 0.26)))
    data[tid] = v0
